      <div class="article-top">
                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">Sleep matters—so much so that six in 10 Americans report craving sleep over sex. The key to rest good enough to forgo sex? It just might be in the mattress. Here&#039;s what you need to know before you go mattress shopping.</div>
